TopicTitle: What do you think of me?

Articles.Content: I just want to know what people generally think of me, in the forum game people haven't seen me around much. Also if this can be put in a better sub-forum, you can move my thread.
To be honest bro, i don't remember seeing you around here. Probably because i only hang out in the space lounge and science labs (Occasionally dabble into other subforums).
I'll be honest, I haven't seen you apart from once or twice in forum games and here, but judging from those encounters you seem like a pretty cool guy, and I like that avatar!
Thank you! Also, that is my cat. I also have just really noticed these subforums and how cool they are the other day after seeing the forum games. I do usually hang around the gameplay areas, though.

"Do you want to know who you are? Don't ask. Act! Action will delineate and define you."

-Thomas Jefferson

Why do you ask?

I just want to know.
I guess I do? I'll just nod my head and say yes. *nods* Yes.

I just want to know.
